":"2b0b1eef5f573742bd97e8c41004c27b7cf0cd75","tid":329086,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中港城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n內地香港城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n內港城</blockquote><br />\n好大浸柒味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efea3eadb861a801b11a800f40c722584309723b","tid":329086,"uid":93940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:47:25.000Z","msg":"越禁越要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌佢老母支那豬收嗲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65b1bbc07dc3a1cfb942a274b2b8b72f7582ae9","tid":329086,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"47、香港、澳門特別行政區的官方機構和制度安排，應按照基本法表述。如「香港特別行政區行政長官」不得說成「香港特別行政區政府行政長官」，「澳門特別行政區立法會」不得說成「澳門特別行政區政府立法會」；香港、澳門實行行政主導的政治體制，不得說成「三權分立」。<br />\n<br />\n48、對港澳反對派自我褒揚的用語和提法要謹慎引用。如不使用「雨傘運動」的說法，應稱為「非法『佔中』」或「違法『佔中』」；<span style=\"color: red;\">不稱「佔中三子」，應稱為「非法『佔中』發起人」，開展輿論鬥爭時可視情稱為「佔中三醜」</span>；不稱天主教香港教區退休主教陳日君等為「榮休主教」，應稱為「前主教」。"},{"pid":"0c00a84c1dec12d0ec1598d0908b74a5354c5570","tid":329086,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:48:37.000Z","msg":"禁多d"},{"pid":"c209c5fca1d9ca0c8ee9fa60aad3b9d203c7f3b4","tid":329086,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中港城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n內地香港城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n內港城</blockquote><br />\n好大浸柒味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人地話唔准一齊講呀<br />\n<br />\n直接叫香港城咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235fc32041babe1fa0c9098f13aba9e0f02a6928","tid":329086,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港中</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecba7aa519f6db7e7269255cd5da46d3ea53c911","tid":329086,"uid":34253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩!"},{"pid":"5bedd8702b1eb569ffff75a8fd226be9046271ae","tid":329086,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:52:02.000Z","msg":"59、對台灣與我名稱相同的大學和文化事業機構，如「清華大學」「故宮博物院」等，應在前面加上台灣、台北或所在地域，如「台灣清華大學」「台灣交通大學」「台北故宮博物院」，一般不使用「台北故宮」的說法。<br />\n<br />\n60、<span style=\"color: red;\">對台灣冠有「國立」字樣的學校和機構，使用時均須去掉「國立」二字。</span>如「國立台灣大學」，應稱「台灣大學」；「XX國小」「XX囯中」，應稱「XX小學」「XX初中」。<br />\n<br />\n原來689政府係先驅 一早做咗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e008012e5f9bb0dc595db908077c93707d23842b","tid":329086,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇撚鳩!</blockquote><br />\n如果大家仲覺得無咩野<br />\n最終都會成為佢地既一份子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ca5f98f4394b8f61153e85bba4d0559ca8068f","tid":329086,"uid":59494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:53:35.000Z","msg":"成百鳩幾條規定真係on撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dc5d557a5879266c8238ffcbacae0e1bc02a1b","tid":329086,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中港城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n內地香港城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n內港城</